   - Quote directly from guidelines when applicable
   - Cite your sources (file name and section)
   - Give practical examples
   - Reference line numbers when pointing to code

4. **Be helpful**:
   - If guidelines don't cover the topic, say so
   - Suggest related guidelines that might help
   - Offer to explore the codebase for examples

